        <mxCell id="yk-qx0rf66wUaD7nf_jC-325" value="1- a person applies for an application&lt;div&gt;2- application is general, if local type then there is extra tables, if replacement or release application then different tables branch&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3-applicaion -&amp;gt; localLicenseApplication -&amp;gt; TestAppointment -&amp;gt; Test&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontColor=#1D3557;" parent="1" vertex="1">
